'''[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿拉伯聯合大公國]]的人權'''受到《[[阿拉伯聯合大公國憲法|阿拉伯聯合大公國憲法]]》的保護及約束，而其賦予人民[[自由|自由]]、[[平等|平等]]、[[法治|法治]]、[[行動自由|行動自由]]、[[宗教信仰|宗教信仰自由]]、[[言論自由|言論自由]]和[[結社|結社]]及就業自由等。<ref>http://www.moca.gov.ae/English/constitution_1_3.asp{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>阿聯酋普遍被認為是[[中東地區|中東地區]]較自由的國家之一，特別是和鄰近的[[沙特阿拉伯|沙特阿拉伯]]以及[[伊朗|伊朗]]相比。<ref name=hrw>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/4861540.stm |title=UAE to Allow Construction Unions |access-date=2010-10-16 |archive-date=2006-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060423122628/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/4861540.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="dubaifire">{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/6277613.stm |title=Dubai Fire Investigation Launched |access-date=2010-10-16 |archive-date=2009-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090929224627/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/middle_east/6277613.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

儘管有憲法的規定，但根據[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]年度人權報告的資料顯示，阿聯酋基本上並沒有產生民主選舉的相關機構、公民沒有更換政府和組成政黨的權利。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2008/nea/119129.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-10-17 |archive-date=2012-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120113120309/http://www.state.gov/g/drl/rls/hrrpt/2008/nea/119129.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>此外，政府會限制[[言論自由|言論自由]]和[[新聞自由|新聞自由]]，當地媒體也會進行「[[自我審查|自我審查]]」來避免節目出現直接批評政府的言論。<ref>[http://archive.gulfnews.com/indepth/pak_emergency/more_stories/10169767.html Gulf News - Pakistani TV channels may move out of Dubai Media City] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080422054301/http://archive.gulfnews.com/indepth/pak_emergency/more_stories/10169767.html |date=2008-04-22 }}</ref><ref>[http://archive.gulfnews.com/articles/07/11/25/10170154.html Gulf News - Geo TV also plans to move out of Dubai] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080401105222/http://archive.gulfnews.com/articles/07/11/25/10170154.html |date=2008-04-01 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.ndtv.com/convergence/ndtv/story.aspx?id=NEWEN20070033255&ch=11/18/2007%208:27:00%20PM NDTV.com - Geo TV hints at options outside of Dubai] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220150253/http://www.ndtv.com/convergence/ndtv/story.aspx?id=NEWEN20070033255&ch=11%2F18%2F2007%208%3A27%3A00%20PM |date=2009-02-20 }}</ref>在當地的[[結社自由|結社自由]]也是受到限制的。

國際人權和勞工權利等相關的公約阿聯酋大多還沒有簽署，包括《[[經濟、社會及文化權利國際公約|經濟、社會及文化權利國際公約]]》、《[[公民權利和政治權利國際公約|公民權利和政治權利國際公約]]》及《[[聯合國禁止酷刑公約|聯合國禁止酷刑公約]]》等。

阿聯酋政府目前正在計畫成立「國家人權委員會」。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.uaeinteract.com/uaeint_misc/pdf_2009/ |title=存档副本 |access-date=2010-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101012020418/http://www.uaeinteract.com/uaeint_misc/pdf_2009/ |archive-date=2010-10-12 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 移民和勞工權利 ==
根據[[英國廣播公司|英國廣播公司]]報導，在杜拜工作的外籍建築工人通常無法得到一個月該有的工資，且他們幾乎無法離開杜拜，因為這樣子不但賺不到錢，還會導致自己負債累累。<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/3694894.stm "Workers' safety queried in Dubai"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/middle_east/3694894.stm |date=20070910165118 }}, by Julia Wheeler, ''BBC News'', September 27, 2004</ref>但其中更重要的因素是，大多數外籍勞工為了進入杜拜，往往得先放棄自己的[[護照|護照]]，因此想要回國變得非常困難。<ref>[http://archive.gulfnews.com/articles/05/09/20/182637.html Ministry cracks the whip] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080209154552/http://archive.gulfnews.com/articles/05/09/20/182637.html |date=2008-02-09 }} Gulf News, 20 Sep 2005</ref>

2005年[[2005年12月|12月]]，印度領事館向杜拜當局提交一份報告，其主題是印度[[僑民|僑民]]在杜拜工作所面臨的問題。報告內容強調延遲支付工資、勞工生活環境和超時工作等問題。2006年3月21日，一群外籍勞工在[[哈里發塔|哈里發塔]]的工地發生暴動，砸毀了施工工具、汽車和辦公桌椅，並要求提高工資和減短工作時間。<ref>[http://www.khaleejtimes.com/DisplayArticle.asp?xfile=data/theuae/2006/March/theuae_March745.xml&section=theuae Labour unrest hampers Burj Dubai work] {{Wayback|url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/DisplayArticle.asp?xfile=data%2Ftheuae%2F2006%2FMarch%2Ftheuae_March745.xml&section=theuae |date=20141129023343 }} Khaleej Times (AP report), 22 March 2006</ref><ref>[http://www.khaleejtimes.com/DisplayArticle.asp?xfile=data/theuae/2006/March/theuae_March779.xml&section=theuae&col= "Burj Dubai workers who protested may be sued"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.khaleejtimes.com/DisplayArticle.asp?xfile=data%2Ftheuae%2F2006%2FMarch%2Ftheuae_March779.xml&section=theuae&col= |date=20130816045524 }} Khaleej Times, 24 March 2006</ref><ref>[http://www.gulfnews.com/indepth/labour/index.html LABOUR IN THE UAE] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080217032430/http://www.gulfnews.com/indepth/labour/index.html |date=2008-02-17 }} Gulf News articles on Labour Law in the UAE, protests, etc</ref>

對外籍勞工的不平等待遇已經引發世界上不少人權組織的關注，並曾經試圖說服政府加入[[國際勞工組織|國際勞工組織]]（International Labour Organization）和開放成立[[工會|工會]]。然而，杜拜當局否認對外籍勞工的不平等待遇，並表示[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]的報告是錯誤的。<ref name=nov1rapecase>[http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/01/world/middleeast/01dubai.html?pagewanted=2&ei=5087&em&en=a89b7518628ebf83&ex=1194062400 In Rape Case, a French Youth Takes On Dubai] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/11/01/world/middleeast/01dubai.html?pagewanted=2&ei=5087&em&en=a89b7518628ebf83&ex=1194062400 |date=20191031182933 }}.  New York Times.  Nov 1, 2007</ref>2006年[[2006年3月|3月]]底，阿聯酋勞工部長Ali al - Kaabi發表聲明：「勞動者將被允許成立工會。」<ref>[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/4861540.stm UAE to allow construction unions] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/business/4861540.stm |date=20060423122628 }} ''BBC News'', March 30, 2006, retrieved April 24, 2006</ref>

